723145f-a.title: Manhattan: St. Nicholas Avenue - 159th Street
723145f-a.text:
974-84 St. Nicholas Avenue (old Kingsbridge Road), east side, between
159th and 160th Streets: Morton Court, an apartment building in
three wings, shown shortly after completion.
About 1909.
Oift of E. M. Jenks.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
